item.title: CVE-2020-4759|2024-09-16T17:49:21.441Z -- ibm -- filenet%20content%20manager
item.description: IBM FileNet Content Manager 5.5.4 and 5.5.5 is potentially vulnerable to CVS Injection. A remote attacker could execute arbitrary commands on the system, caused by improper validation of csv file contents. IBM X-Force ID: 188736.
